    <div style="margin-left: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            This project was our attempt to solidy our knowledge on dealing with relatoinal databases and linking up a website with a DBMS (Database Mangement System) - in this case, we are specifically making use of MariaDB.</br>
        <ul style="margin-left: 3rem;">
            <li>As of now, the website allows users to register students, add schedules, and courses for each of the students.</li>
            <li>It also allows users to register professors, classrooms, and courses.</li>
            <li>Users can also view all the schedules in the entire database.</li>
            <li>Each page also has helpful instructions and links to help users get familiar with the site faster</li>
        </ul>
        </p>

